  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "As a use case I'd like to be able to deploy charts on separate namespaces and have a way to `helm list` a specific namespace. Currently there is no easy way of doing that.\r\n\r\nI don't want to clutter helm list with more columns but this seems an important info on a multi-namespace cluster. Maybe we can add this with an optional flag (something similar to `kubectl -o wide` - related to #1534 on formatting subject).\r\n\r\nA filtering field could be something of sort:\r\n\r\n`helm list -n kube-system`\r\n\r\nin order to show only releases inside the kube-system namespace.\r\n",
